== Umwuga ==
Kaka n'''i''' rwiyemezamirimo windashyikirwa mu Rwanda. yatangije isosiyete yitwa Rwanda Chic - umurima worora inkoko kuva ziva ku isoko. Mu Rwanda umuryango w’ubucuruzi w’abagore benshi, Nuriat afatwa nkumujyanama numuyobozi witsinda. Umujyanama ushakishwa, Nuriat atoza abandi gutangira no guteza imbere ubucuruzi bwabo. Ishyaka rye risanzwe rimufasha guhuza abantu vuba no kubagira ingaruka mubikorwa.

